snippet.title: Pop-Up Pilgrims
snippet.description:
Floating Cloud God and his devoted pilgrims have a big adventure ahead! 

Put on your Playstation VR headset and discover a world of pop-up islands, colourful characters, and deadly demons, all uniquely presented as 2D graphics in a wrap-around 3D space.

Visuals: Army of Trolls @armyoftrolls
Music: Samuel Baker @thefinalform
